{"tid":2354127,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"永久居留申請遭拒絕  聽命中共 危及國安 華商面臨逐出澳洲","createTime":"2021-01-05T08:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T08:40:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"94366b00744bab20f5fa5f4d0675b1969ffd2912","tid":2354127,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:34:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210105/NLKMMMR5PZAWTNFSSU6A35ND6M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210105%2FNLKMMMR5PZAWTNFSSU6A35ND6M%2F&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAG7KDDpXBBweeKWShnQU3kRY%3D&h=2287f78a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210105%2FNLKMMMR5PZAWTNFSSU6A35ND6M%2F&h=282f1d36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210105/NLKMMMR5PZAWTNFSSU6A35ND6M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n永久居留申請遭拒絕 <br />\n聽命中共 危及國安 華商面臨逐出澳洲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NDgFZ22niM2Va4P2QKj1V9Ysg7M=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZTQ2NHLEC5BW5EXHXJL6WANNTI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNDgFZ22niM2Va4P2QKj1V9Ysg7M%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZTQ2NHLEC5BW5EXHXJL6WANNTI.jpg&h=3135052d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■劉輝峰(右)與中國駐澳洲大使成競業合照。<br />\n<br />\n中澳緊張關係不斷升溫，澳洲安全情報組織（ASIO）調查居於墨爾本的中國商人劉輝峰，認為他對澳洲國家安全構成威脅，已拒絕其永久居留申請，未來很有可能被遣返中國。劉接受澳媒訪問稱，被評估有「安全風險」的原因，與他擔任受中國領使館指令的華人協會會長有關。中國駐墨爾本總領事館昨發聲明，強調不會干涉任何國家內政，敦促澳媒停止抹黑中國。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲廣播公司（ABC）報道，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kP54RMLL1oyBNqiNC8NSzY3a_Co=/1573x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QWSHDBRXPZF27B3CVCUEIN3HAU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkP54RMLL1oyBNqiNC8NSzY3a_Co%3D%2F1573x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQWSHDBRXPZF27B3CVCUEIN3HAU.jpg&h=84131800&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■蘇卡爾曾寄聖誕卡給劉輝峰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n收使館撥款查華人活動<br />\n<br />\n報道指，澳洲聯邦警察證實正與ASIO反海外干預工作組展開聯合行動，共同調查劉輝峰，但未有進一步評論。<br />\n<br />\n劉輝峰接受ABC訪問稱，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n報道表示，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐墨爾本總領事館官網訊息，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華領館促澳媒停抹黑<br />\n<br />\n中國駐墨爾本總領事館昨日發聲明批評，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲廣播公司<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uqzni-vBrb73-wQ7cILGpT27RFY=/480x383/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KPN6DU2OLRB7BHG5BKT6SZKZKE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fuqzni-vBrb73-wQ7cILGpT27RFY%3D%2F480x383%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKPN6DU2OLRB7BHG5BKT6SZKZKE.gif&h=5e985033&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■劉輝峰透過自由黨議員廖嬋娥認識不少澳洲政壇人物，包括澳洲前總理特恩布爾。"},{"pid":"4e6f54d5834aaa111039a2901db183d069d23030","tid":2354127,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:40:40.000Z","msg":"人大啲親戚呢？"}]}